&nbsp;
<h2>
Aldo Spinelli, entrepreneur in the logistic and real estate sector, for which the house arrests were taken, is disputed corruption against Signorini and Toti. For entrepreneur Roberto Spinelli, to whom corruption is disputed against the President of the Region, the interdictive measure of the temporary prohibition of exercising the business and professional activity has been arranged. The same precautionary measure for Mauro Vianello, an entrepreneur working in the field of the Port of Genoa, accused of corruption against Signorini; for Francesco Moncada, advisor of administration of Esselunga spa, which is contested the same crime against Toti.<br> Matteo Cozzani, head of cabinet of the president of the Liguria Region, is under house arrest for 'election competition', aggravated by the hypothesis that the crime has been committed to facilitate the activity of the Mafia association Cosa Nostra, in particular of Cammarata. Cozzani is also investigated for corruption for the exercise of the function.<br> Arturo Angelo Testa and Italo Maurizio Testa, representatives of the Riesine Community of Genoa, are recipients of the obligation to dwell in the Municipality of Boltiere, with the charge of exacerbated electoral corruption.<br> The same crime is challenged to Venanzio Maurici, recipient of the obligation to submit to the judicial police.

