AGI - They do not stop at the Alta >e during the escape they invest a policeman: two minors arrested for official public resistance and aggravated injuries in Catania>, by agents of the Flying Squad and Mobile Team. The boys, on board a scooter >, did not respect the Alt by fleeing. A chase began in Kennedy Avenue, in Playa area, informing colleagues engaged in other places of control. The police again undertook the Alt, but the driver instead of stopping overwhelmed a state police officer, dropping him to the ground and storing him.
&nbsp;
The pursuit, in which more Volanti were engaged, continued through the streets of the city. The police helicopter managed to "enter" the scooter by means of a camera on board documenting all phases of the escape, so as to provide precise indications to all crews. Arrived near via Ammiraglio Caracciolo>, thanks to a motorcyclists maneuver of the Flying Team and the Mobile Team, the two fugitives were forced to stop.» From the investigations carried out the scooter has been without insurance cover > and periodic review >. The driver was without a driver's license. High sanctions amounted to approximately 6 thousand euros. The policeman overwhelmed during the escape was immediately rescued by the staff of 118 and after a rest period he will be able to resume the operational service. The pm at the Tribunal for Minors has arranged that the two young people were accompanied to the first reception center pending the validation hearing, following which the arrests were validated and the two issued with obligation to comply with different prescriptions.

